            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1650990884344-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1650990884344-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>fable mushrooms </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>ground cumin</strong> and <strong>smoked paprika</strong> with 2/3 of the <strong>cider vinegar</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>agave </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Pour in 100ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [180ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> (save the rest for later!) and give everything a good mix up, then put the dish in the oven for 25 min or until most of the liquid has been absorbed and the fable mushrooms are slightly crispy</p>",
